    "name": {
      "zh": "GPNVG-18夜视仪",
      "en": "L3Harris GPNVG-18 night vision goggles"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "GPNVG-18",
      "en": "GPNVG-18"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "全景夜视镜GPNVG-18（Ground Panoramic Night Vision Google）。 该夜视仪与其他夜视仪的主要区别在于它有四个独立的EOP，每只眼睛两个。两个中央EOP朝向前方，另外两个则从中心朝向外。这一创新的解决方案允许将视野范围扩大到97度。",
      "en": "The GPNVG-18 (Ground Panoramic Night Vision Goggle) panoramic night vision goggles. The cardinal difference of this NVG from the others is the presence of four separate image intensifier tubes, two for each eye. Two Central IITs are directed forward, while two more are directed outward from the center. This innovative solution allowed to expand the field of view to 97 degrees."
    },
